I also grateful to Rusty
and Carol Marchetto,

00:19:58.829 --> 00:20:00.983
about whom you already heard today,

00:20:00.983 --> 00:20:03.766
for really sharing with us chimp IPS cells

00:20:03.766 --> 00:20:05.574
very early in the game.

00:20:05.574 --> 00:20:08.763
Our mouse genetics
collaborator, Licia Selleri,

00:20:08.763 --> 00:20:12.511
and also our human
phenotyping and GWAS team,

00:20:12.511 --> 00:20:15.486
Peter Claes, Seth
Weinberg, and Mark Shriver,

00:20:15.486 --> 00:20:17.192
thank you very much.

