00:57:32.770 --> 00:57:35.292
but she was assisted by many people

00:57:35.292 --> 00:57:37.956
and many people in my lab,

00:57:37.956 --> 00:57:39.990
at least there's four people listed here

00:57:39.990 --> 00:57:43.115
are involved in current
aspect of the project.

